OL,3,CGuernsey to sail ahead with Brittany
OL,4,CFerries contract
OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey aim to publish
OL,7,Fschedules for their 2025 ferry service
OL,8,Fthis week as they forge ahead with
OL,9,Fdrafting a Guernsey-only contract with
OL,10,FBrittany Ferries.
OL,12,FIn an update on the Committee for
OL,13,FEconomic Development's contract talks
OL,14,Fwith Brittany Ferries, The States say
OL,15,Fthat they aim to grant their licence
OL,16,Fto Brittany Ferries, subject to final
OL,17,Fdiscussions and relevant approvals.
