OL,6,FThe States of Guernsey has stipulated
OL,7,Fthat the contract also hopes to grant
OL,8,Fpermission for Condor Ferries to
OL,9,Foperate services.
OL,11,FThe States of Guernsey reiterated that
OL,12,Fa new contract will ensure the same
OL,13,Fcapacity for freight and passenger
OL,14,Fservices as there is currently, adding
OL,15,Fthat customers will not see "any
OL,16,Fnotable increase in price".
OL,18,FStates of Guernsey also says that
OL,19,FBrittany Ferries has guaranteed its
OL,20,Ffull financial and operational
OL,21,Fservices.
