OL,3,CGuernsey to sail ahead with Brittany
OL,4,CFerries contract
OL,6,FPresident of the Committee for
OL,7,FEconomic Development, Deputy Neil
OL,8,FInder, says: "The final discussions in
OL,9,Frelation to the draft contract are
OL,10,Ftaking place this week. As soon as we
OL,11,Fhave an agreed draft contract the
OL,12,Fschedule will be published.
OL,14,F"These types of contracts are complex,
OL,15,Fbut I have made it clear to officers
OL,16,Fthat I want the work done to enable us
OL,17,Fto publish the schedules this week,
OL,18,Fnot next week."
