OL,6,FBrittany Ferries chairman Jean-Marc
OL,7,FRoue has also released a statement
OL,8,Fexpressing his "surprise and concern"
OL,9,Fover Jersey's decision not to accept
OL,10,Ftheir bid and responding to what he
OL,11,Fcalls "damaging comments" from the
OL,12,FStates of Jersey and media reports.
OL,14,FHe explains: "The company I chair
OL,15,Fexists because its only guide is
OL,16,Fcustomer satisfaction. The financial
OL,17,Fbenefits of our activities are totally
OL,18,Freinvested in the company.
