OL,6,F"(Brittany Ferries' farmer-
OL,7,Fshareholders) aim at the outset was
OL,8,Fthe same as it is today: to enrich the
OL,9,Fregions in which it operates, to
OL,10,Fconnect people, and to facilitate
OL,11,Ftrade.
OL,13,F"It is this mindset that will be
OL,14,Fbrought to Guernsey over the next 15
OL,15,Fyears - and is the promise for
OL,16,Fbusinesses and the public in Jersey.
