OL,3,CGuernsey to sail ahead with Brittany
OL,4,CFerries contract
OL,6,F"I should also point out that, never
OL,7,Fin our 52-year history have we
OL,8,Fabandoned a ferry line or a service to
OL,9,Fa region for lack of profitability. We
OL,10,Fare a highly-respected company and we
OL,11,Fentered this competition in good faith
OL,12,Fto continue our service to islanders."
OL,14,FMonsieur Roue has confirmed that the
OL,15,Fcompany will respond to the new Jersey-
OL,16,Fonly bid process.
OL,18,FThe Committee for Economic Development
OL,19,Falso clarified how the tender process
OL,20,Fled to selecting Brittany Ferries as
OL,21,Fits preferred bidder.
