OL,4,CFerries contract
OL,6,FThey say that the Invitation for
OL,7,FTender process was run by both
OL,8,FGuernsey and Jersey over 10 months,
OL,9,Fbeing closed by senior officers in
OL,10,Fboth islands.
OL,12,FIt is reiterated that they confirmed
OL,13,FDFDS' bid received a legal fail after
OL,14,Fbeing confirmed by the States of
OL,15,FJersey, with Brittany submitting a
OL,16,F"very strong" bid that "pass all
OL,17,Frequirements (...) including
OL,18,Ffinancial".
