OL,4,CFerries contract
OL,6,FThe Committee say that they "followed
OL,7,Fthe tender process to its rightful
OL,8,Fconclusion given the circumstances and
OL,9,Fdid not consider it fair or
OL,10,Fappropriate to take any other course
OL,11,Fof action".
OL,13,FDeputy Inder adds: "The Committee
OL,14,Fmaintains the view that the tender
OL,15,Fprocess was undertaken correctly, in
OL,16,Fline with the agreed rules and
OL,17,Fmethodology, and that a preferred
OL,18,Fbidder could be appointed."
