OL,6,FOn Condor's prior financial
OL,7,Fchallenges, Deputy Inder states:
OL,8,F"Condor's financial issues at the end
OL,9,Fof 2023 were well known and
OL,10,Fimportantly occurred when it was owned
OL,11,Fby a different company ` Columbia
OL,12,FThreadneedle.
OL,14,F"No funding was provided by the States
OL,15,Fof Guernsey at the time and Brittany
OL,16,FFerries subsequently became the
OL,17,Fmajority shareholder of Condor,
OL,18,Fbringing increased financial security."
